HEADWORD: orthoepy
<hw>or"tho*e*py</hw> <pr>(⟦ocir⟧r"th⟦osl⟧*⟦esl⟧*p⟦ycr⟧; 277)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>'orqoe`peia</grk>; <grk>'orqo`s</grk> right
